snippet.title: Jupiter & Mars - E3 2018 Trailer | PS4, PS VR
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/jupiter-and-mars-ps4/

Take a brand new look at the underwater adventure game Jupiter & Mars for PlayStation 4 and PlayStation VR. Play as Jupiter, a dolphin with enhanced echolocation powers, and her partner Mars and encounter magnificent creatures known as the Elders who guide you on your journey. Featuring an amazing, futuristic underwater world set to an evocative soundtrack, Jupiter & Mars is unlike any adventure game you have ever seen or heard.

https://www.tigertron.eco/jam 

“JUPITER & MARS” is a trademark of Tigertron, Inc.
